## [1.0.0] - 2025-10-23

### Added
- Initial release of VAULT (Virtual Attack Utilty Lab Terminal)
- Interactive CLI shell with command history and tab completion
- Multi-cloud support for AWS, Azure, and GCP
- Lab deployment and lifecycle management (init, plan, deploy, destroy)
- Lab discovery and fuzzy search capabilities
- Terraform state management and metadata tracking
- CSP tool installation guidance (aws-cli, azure-cli, gcloud, terraform)
- Active deployment tracking and status monitoring
- Lab output management with sensitive value protection
- Configuration templates for AWS, Azure, and GCP

### Infrastructure
- Modular Terraform configurations
- Shared VPC and VM modules
- State isolation per lab deployment
- Auto-shutdown tags for cost management

